title: Unreal Engine 4 - Compiled Build
description:
Unreal Engine 4 - Build 4.0.1



Includes all source files (requires Visual Studio 2013).


This is a compiled build of the editor to take the leg work out of compiling the engine yourself.


How to install:

Extract all and run UE4Client.exe located in Engine/Binaries/win64 folder.

-That's it!!


First load up will take a bit of time, be patient. The engine has to compile all the shaders and materials.

As always, block the program in your firewall.

Enjoy the new Unreal Engine 4!!
